---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aboutImg from '@assets/about.webp';
import CrosshairIcon from '@assets/icons/crosshair-2-line.svg';
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <Image class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-xl rounded-3xl" src={aboutImg} alt="About" priority />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <CrosshairIcon class="fill-primary-500 h-8 w-8 shrink-0 sm:h-10 sm:w-10" aria-hidden="true" />
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">About Me</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-muted text-base sm:text-lg">
              I'm <strong>Safraz Razik</strong> — founder of <strong>Zetmel</strong>, an AI-accelerated software engineering studio.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted text-base sm:text-lg">
              I'm a software professional with 15+ years in full-stack development, project leadership, and startup co-founding. My expertise spans modern JavaScript frameworks (React, Vue, TypeScript, Next.js), backend systems (Node.js, PHP, Python), and enterprise platforms like Oracle Commerce Cloud and Oracle Storefront Framework.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted text-base sm:text-lg">
              I run local LLM environments (Ollama, OpenCode, Claude Code), evaluate coding models for quality and task fit, and use structured prompting workflows to coordinate multi-stage development — all while maintaining production standards through technical audits and recovery sprints.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted text-base sm:text-lg">
              I've delivered solutions at Motorola Solutions and startups alike, co-founded ventures, built open-source tools (<a href="https://github.com/safrazik/vue-file-agent" class="text-link">Vue File Agent</a>, <a href="https://github.com/rockplate/rockplate" class="text-link">Rockplate</a>), and contributed across web, mobile, and desktop platforms.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="border-subtle rounded-3xl border p-6">
            <dt class="text-base">Experience</dt>
            <dd class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight">15+ years</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="border-subtle rounded-3xl border p-6">
            <dt class="text-base">Location</dt>
            <dd class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight">Sri Lanka</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
